folder: Bruckner Boulevard & Elder Avenue, Bronx, NY
text:
Pedestrian over-pass at Bruckner Boulevard and Elder Avenue, Bronx, N.Y., for school crossing.

Steel girders 36 feet, 260 lbs. per foot. Center span 185 feet

Designed by A. Narnow, A.B. P.E.
about 1960
